# ─── App state / config (private) ──────────────────────────────────────
# All app-managed state lives here: the db, GUI config, exported login cookies,
# the persistent X.com browser profile, and runtime copies of the site registry
# (the pristine seeds are tracked in assets/). Everything here is per-user.
config/
*.cookies

# ─── Generated runtime state (root) ────────────────────────────────────
# Download queue / history / failures — kept in the root as an editable input.
links_to_download.txt
links_downloaded.txt
link_failed.txt

# ─── Downloaded content ────────────────────────────────────────────────
videos/
downloads/
*.part
*.ytdl
*.mp4
*.mkv
*.webm
*.m4a
*.jpg
*.png

# ─── Build artifacts (PyInstaller) ─────────────────────────────────────
build/
dist/
*.exe
*.app/
BulkDownloaderGUI-mac.zip

# ─── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ─── Editor / OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
